charlie chan in the trap is a 1946 crime film directed by howard bretherton . the main premise is two members of a show troupe are murdered , and charlie chan is called in to solve the case . this was sidney toler 's final film and his final one as the detective charlie chan , his 22nd of the series . stricken with cancer during his last few films , toler was so physically weak during filming that he could hardly walk or say his lines &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; .